<concept xml:lang="en-us" id="exclusion">
<title>Ditaval Exclusion</title>
<shortdesc>This checks on ditaval exclusion for ph, p, section, fig,
image, table, and xref. <ph platform="linux" audience="expert">This
version is for the <term keyref="OS"/> platform and an expert audience.</ph><ph
 platform="windows" audience="beginner">This page is for <term keyref="OS"/>
beginners, not for <?dtall keyrefbranch="Revisited" ?><term keyref="OS"/>.</ph></shortdesc>
