<section platform="windows">
<title>Windows Information</title>
<p audience="expert">This para is for experts only, and should not be
present.</p>
<p audience="beginner">This para is for beginners. <ph audience="expert">Except for this
sentence. </ph>It should remain.</p>
<ul>
<li>First item.</li>
<li audience="expert">Excluded item.</li>
<li audience="beginner">Included item.</li>
<li>Last item.</li>
</ul>
</section>
